# MessageAI

A modern, cross-platform messaging application built with Flutter and Supabase, featuring real-time messaging, typing indicators, image sharing, and offline support.

## âœ¨ Features

- ðŸ” **Secure Authentication** - Email/password authentication with Supabase
- ðŸ’¬ **Real-time Messaging** - Instant message delivery with Supabase Realtime
- âŒ¨ï¸ **Typing Indicators** - See when others are typing with animated indicators
- ðŸ“· **Image Sharing** - Upload and share images in conversations
- ðŸ‘¤ **Profile Pictures** - Custom avatar support with image upload
- ðŸ“§ **Add by Email** - Add participants to conversations using email addresses
- ðŸ“± **Offline Support** - Queue messages when offline, auto-sync when back online
- ðŸŽ¨ **Modern UI** - Burnt orange theme 
- ðŸ“– **Message Previews** - See the last message in each conversation
